{"parse":{"title":"Raw Brilliant Smallfish","pageid":37913,"wikitext":{"*":"<noinclude>__NOTOC__</noinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_08\n|name=Raw Brilliant Smallfish\n|quality=common\n|charges=1\n|stack=20\n|effect=<u>Use</u>: Restores 30 health over 15 sec. Must remain seated while eating.\n|sell={{Cost|c=1}} each\n|ilvl=5\n}}<noinclude>\nA '''Raw Brilliant Smallfish''' can be eaten without cooking, but it's not as good.\n{{clrl}}\n==Source==\nThis fish can be caught by [[fishing]] in the waters of low level zones, as well as in the waters of the capitals.\nFor instance, it can be found in [[Loch Modan]] among other zones.\n\n==Raw Brilliant Smallfish as an Ingredient==\n\n===Cooking===\n*[[Brilliant Smallfish]]\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|6291}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/raw_brilliant_smallfish.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft food items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft cooking ingredient items]]\n\n</noinclude>"}}}